name: Modway_Silhouette_Modern_White_Dining_Chairs_(Set_of_2)
reviews: They are super cute! Mixed them with similar chairs with oval shape and they look incredible! Fancy feel without a crazy price tag! They make my place look upscale. Assembly was simple I'm a 23 year old female and had no problems putting them together!
Elegant and easy to clean. Good quality. I bought two for my kitchen island and they look fab.

I didn't pay to much for the chairs. I purchased 6 of them about a month ago Maybe Don't even think i have had them for a month(due to having to be delivered) I already notice that at least 1 or 2 of the chairs are cracked on the bottom of the chairs. Noticed this due to when i leaned my knee on the chair it sounded like it split so i looked underneath the chair and it is cracked. This is the first time I have used OverStock and it will be the Last. Prime example, That you get what you Pay for.
Great quality and better after getting the chairs.
These chairs are even more beautiful in person. Love them comfortable and classy modern look!!!
I purchased the Modway Silhouette Modern White Dining chairs for my daughter. Very Impressed with the classy look and very sturdy
Beautiful and classy. Makes my dinning room look expensive
description:
These Silhouette modern dining chairs feature graceful curves that whisper elegance from every position. A softly tapered back and rounded hardwood legs lend distinguished support to these hourglass-shaped chairs.
